    dc:creator "James Wilder Orr; Katherine Pearson Maslenikov" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Two New Variegated Snailfishes of the Genus Careproctus (Teleostei: Scorpaeniformes: Liparidae) from the Aleutian Islands, Alaska" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269706>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269705>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269707>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269708> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269706>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Pectoral girdles of two new species of Careproctus and similar species: (A) Careproctus comus, new species, UW 111834, 72.8 mm SL; (B) Careproctus faunus, new species, UW 113646, 96 mm SL; (C) Temnocora candida, UW 111870, 77.9 mm SL; (D) Careproctus bowersianus, UW 111871, 100 mm SL. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269705>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Two new species of Careproctus, Temnocora candida, and C. bowersianus from the Aleutian Islands: (A) Careproctus comus, new species, holotype, UW 111841, 78.9 mm SL, male; (B) Careproctus faunus, new species, holotype, UW 111867, 101.9 mm SL, male; (C) Temnocora candida, UW 111862, 67.8 mm SL, female; (D) Careproctus bowersianus, UW 111871, 90.0 mm SL, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269705/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269707>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Distribution of two new species of Careproctus from the Aleutian Islands based on all known material: Careproctus comus, new species (open circle), Careproctus faunus, new species (solid circle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269707/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269708>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Scatter plots of significant morphometric characters distinguishing Careproctus comus, new species, and Careproctus faunus, new species: (A) Interorbital width; (B) Snout length; (C) Anal-fin connection to caudal-fin length; (D) Caudal-fin base depth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

